# Keep the build context small and, crucially, keep host state/secrets out of
# the image: data/ holds the local gheart.json (with stored App creds) and
# server/data holds the local brain. Prod uses the Fly volume (/data) instead.
node_modules
dist
data
server/data
.git
.github
.claude
.firecrawl
docs
scratchpad
*.log
npm-debug.log*
.DS_Store
# Note: fnox.toml is intentionally NOT ignored — the entrypoint decrypts it.
